data.description: Really nice location in Shady Cove on large mature lot. Clean 2 bedroom, 1 bath home with 1000 square feet. Would be easy to add on to this home and have split bedroom floor plan, or you could also build a 900 square foot ADU.  Home features a large living room with woodstove hookup, plus a dining area & indoor utility. Detached 560 square foot garage has a 1/2 bath. Large covered patio and carport, plus circular driveway with plenty of parking for cars, boats and RV's. One seller is a licensed realtor in the state of Oregon and is a co-listing agent.
